    {
      "id": "tpt-oneliner",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "One-Liner",
      "position": {
        "x": 400,
        "y": -180
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 140,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## The Pitch\n\n> **\"Figma meets ChatGPT for visual thinking.\"**\n\nDescribe what you want to an AI → AI generates a graph → Paste into Twilite → Graph appears instantly.\n\nNo manual clicking and dragging. Just think, describe, and see.",
