    {
      "id": "tpt-possibilities",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "What You Can Build",
      "position": {
        "x": 1000,
        "y": -180
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 560,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## What You Can Build\n\n*The graph has no ceiling.*\n\n🗺️ **Thinking & Planning**\nRoadmaps, mind maps, knowledge bases, research notes, decision trees\n\n📊 **Dashboards**\nLive data nodes pulling from APIs, databases, spreadsheets — updated in real time\n\n⚡ **Automation**\nEvent nodes, trigger nodes, action nodes. Build Zapier-style workflows visually.\n\n🤖 **AI Agents**\nPrompt nodes, model nodes, memory nodes. Wire up multi-step reasoning.\n\n📱 **Interactive Docs**\nForms, calculators, configurators. The graph responds to user input.\n\n🎮 **Games & Simulations**\nState machines, behavior trees, game logic. Nodes are game objects.\n\n🔌 **Integrations**\nAny API becomes a node. Any webhook becomes a trigger. **The graph talks to everything.**\n\n---\n\n*Today it's notes and roadmaps. Tomorrow it's anything you can imagine.*",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
