    {
      "id": "tpt-solution",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "The Solution",
      "position": {
        "x": 400,
        "y": 0
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## The Solution\n\nMake the graph a **first-class artifact**:\n\n✅ **Portable `.node` files** — JSON you can store anywhere\n\n✅ **Stable IDs** — nodes and edges have identity across time\n\n✅ **AI mutation contract** — deltas, not rewrites; validation, not chaos\n\n✅ **Web distribution** — URLs, embeds, GitHub, templates\n\n✅ **Progressive complexity** — start with notes, evolve to workflows, end with execution\n\n---\n\n**The result:** A graph that survives time, tools, and assistants. Your thinking becomes infrastructure.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
