    {
      "id": "tpt-artifact",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "The Artifact",
      "position": {
        "x": -200,
        "y": 420
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 380,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## The Artifact\n\nA Twilite graph is a `.node` file:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"fileVersion\": \"1.0\",\n  \"metadata\": { ... },\n  \"settings\": { ... },\n  \"viewport\": { ... },\n  \"nodes\": [ ... ],\n  \"edges\": [ ... ],\n  \"clusters\": [ ... ]\n}\n```\n\n**Properties:**\n- 📁 Portable JSON (store in Git, S3, anywhere)\n- 🔑 Stable node/edge IDs (meaningful diffs)\n- 🎨 Settings + viewport (opens exactly as saved)\n- 🔌 Plugin extensions (namespaced custom data)\n- 📄 Optional embedded document\n\n**Goal:** A graph that survives time, tools, and AI assistants.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
