    {
      "id": "tpt-ai",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "AI Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": 400,
        "y": 420
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 380,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## AI Contract\n\n**The key innovation:** A mutation protocol that lets AI safely edit graphs.\n\n### Actions\n```\ncreate   → add nodes/edges\nupdate   → modify existing by ID\ndelete   → remove by ID\nbatch    → multiple operations atomically\n```\n\n### Principles\n- **Deltas over rewrites** — AI sends changes, not full snapshots\n- **Validation gates** — malformed commands fail gracefully\n- **Minimal payloads** — positions/ports optional; editor fills in\n- **Dry run mode** — preview impact before applying\n\n### Outcome\nPaste JSON from ChatGPT/Claude → graph appears instantly → AI can evolve it coherently over time.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
