    {
      "id": "tpt-workflow",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "The Workflow",
      "position": {
        "x": 1000,
        "y": 420
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 380,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## The Workflow\n\n### For Humans\n1. **Describe** what you want to an AI\n2. **AI generates** graph JSON\n3. **Paste** into Twilite (Ctrl+V)\n4. **Graph appears** — edit, extend, save\n\n### For AI Agents\n1. **Read** `.node` files from filesystem/URLs\n2. **Reason** about structure and relationships\n3. **Write** delta mutations (create/update/delete)\n4. **Validate** changes before applying\n\n### For Teams\n1. **Store** graphs in Git\n2. **Review** changes as diffs in PRs\n3. **Share** via URLs or embeds\n4. **Remix** templates and patterns",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
