    {
      "id": "tpt-web",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Web Distribution",
      "position": {
        "x": 400,
        "y": 860
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Web Distribution\n\nGraphs live on the web:\n\n🔗 **Linkable**\n- Direct URLs to `.node` files\n- Query params: `?doc=https://...`\n- GitHub raw URLs work natively\n\n📦 **Shareable**\n- Export/import JSON\n- Embed in docs/wikis\n- Read-only viewer for publishing\n\n🎨 **Remixable**\n- Template gallery\n- Fork and modify\n- Community patterns\n\n---\n\n**The format travels.** The editor is just the best way to interact with it.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
