    {
      "id": "tpt-moat",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Defensibility",
      "position": {
        "x": 1000,
        "y": 860
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## What Makes It Defensible\n\n*\"Better graph\" isn't the pitch. It's the mechanism.*\n\n### The Moat\n- **Artifact standardization** — compatibility guarantees\n- **AI mutation contract** — deltas, validation, safety\n- **Layout intelligence** — small payloads, professional output\n- **Plugin contract** — extensible without fragmentation\n- **Git-native workflows** — diffs, PRs, history\n\n---\n\n**This is a governance + workflow moat**, not a model moat.\n\nCompetitors can copy features. They can't easily copy the contract that makes AI collaboration safe and predictable.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
