    {
      "id": "tpt-wedges",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "First Wedges",
      "position": {
        "x": 100,
        "y": 1280
      },
      "width": 700,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## First Wedges\n\n*Start with jobs that are true today:*\n\n### 🗺️ Roadmaps as Artifacts\nPlanning docs that can be versioned, reviewed, and evolved.\n\n### 📝 AI-to-Graph Note Taking\n\"Turn this conversation into a diagram\" — instant structure.\n\n### 🔍 PR-Reviewable Graphs\nChanges as deltas. Review graphs like you review code.\n\n### 🧠 Agent Domain Memory\nDurable state for long-running AI work. Graphs as context.\n\n---\n\n**Success metric:** A stranger can create a useful graph in 5 minutes and come back tomorrow to find it exactly as they left it.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
