    {
      "id": "tpt-usecases",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Use Cases",
      "position": {
        "x": 860,
        "y": 1280
      },
      "width": 700,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Use Cases\n\n| Category | Examples |\n|----------|----------|\n| **Visual Thinking** | Brainstorming, mind maps, ideation |\n| **Knowledge Graphs** | Concepts, relationships, hierarchies |\n| **Project Planning** | Roadmaps, timelines, dependencies |\n| **Learning** | Study diagrams, concept maps |\n| **Research** | Notes, citations, connections |\n| **Storytelling** | Narrative structures, character webs |\n| **Architecture** | System design, component maps |\n| **Decision Making** | Pros/cons, options, tradeoffs |\n\n---\n\n**Common thread:** Any time you need to *see* how things connect, Twilite can help — and AI can help you build it.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
